::KitKat::

She smiled at him as he kissed her.  "No. I will not take command.  Not 
untill I know how the tides or war are flowing. Besides, the current leader 
may be a strong and wise leader. After all, don't you remember that I became 
leader just because Megatron left us to die and I couldn't leave the pack 
leaderless.  So no, I'll wait to see if my leadership is needed."
She wondered who the leader of the new pack was.
